snippet.title: POWERWASH SIMULATOR VR OFFICIAL LAUNCH TRAILER | PLAY YOUR WAY | META QUEST
snippet.description:
PowerWash Simulator VR is out now! 💦

Play solo, or play with friends, play with POWER, or play with precision. Play YOUR way in VR and express yourself on Meta Quest 2, pro and 3! 

Enjoy two brand-new unique features just for the VR version: an interactive toolbelt for your nozzles and a van menu where players can change their outfits and equipment!

Play today: https://bit.ly/46cx2CR

Follow PowerWash Simulator socials! 
Twitter: https://bit.ly/TwitterPWS
TikTok: https://bit.ly/PWSTikTok

#VR #PowerWashSimulator #Meta #Quest #VRGaming
